a\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Jersey\"}, {\"begin\": 1413, \"end\": 1417, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_of_Bethany\", \"score\": 0.999011684756094, \"rank\": 0.000513842112373349, \"text\": \"Mary\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_of_Bethany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_of_Bethany\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"parents\", \"from\": 1394, \"to\": 1401}, {\"ngram\": \"Willie\", \"from\": 1402, \"to\": 1408}, {\"ngram\": \"track and field athletes\", \"from\": 1447, \"to\": 1471}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her father, a semi-finalist in the 400m 1984 Olympic Trials and her mother, a 2:12 half-miler at Cardinal O'Hara High School where she ran on the boys' team.\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1630, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her father\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1483}, {\"ngram\": \"finalist\", \"from\": 1492, \"to\": 1500}, {\"ngram\": \"the 400m 1984 Olympic Trials\", \"from\": 1504, \"to\": 1532}, {\"ngram\": \"her mother\", \"from\": 1537, \"to\": 1547}, {\"ngram\": \"a 2:12 half-miler\", \"from\": 1549, \"to\": 1566}, {\"ngram\": \"Cardinal O'Hara High School\", \"from\": 1570, \"to\": 1597}, {\"ngram\": \"the boys' team\", \"from\": 1615, \"to\": 1629}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It should be no surprise that McLaughlin-Levrone, along with her older brother and sister, followed in their parents' footsteps and despite her siblings' prowess for running, her father said it was clear that 'Sydney was a little special'.\", \"from\": 1632, \"to\": 1871, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1842, \"end\": 1848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9999641082697247, \"rank\": 2.9760447373699013e-05, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no surprise\", \"from\": 1645, \"to\": 1656}, {\"ngram\": \"McLaughlin-Levrone\", \"from\": 1662, \"to\": 1680}, {\"ngram\": \"her older brother\", \"from\": 1693, \"to\": 1710}, {\"ngram\": \"sister\", \"from\": 1715, \"to\": 1721}, {\"ngram\": \"their parents' footsteps\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1759}, {\"ngram\": \"her siblings' prowess\", \"from\": 1772, \"to\": 1793}, {\"ngram\": \"her father\", \"from\": 1807, \"to\": 1817}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the national junior championships in 2014, McLaughlin finished a close second in the 400 metre hurdles with a time of 55.63s - a national high school freshman record.\", \"from\": 1873, \"to\": 2042, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the national junior championships\", \"from\": 1876, \"to\": 1909}, {\"ngram\": \"McLaughlin\", \"from\": 1919, \"to\": 1929}, {\"ngram\": \"a close second\", \"from\": 1939, \"to\": 1953}, {\"ngram\": \"the 400 metre hurdles\", \"from\": 1957, \"to\": 1978}, {\"ngram\": \"a time\", \"from\": 1984, \"to\": 1990}, {\"ngram\": \"55.63s - a national high school freshman record\", \"from\": 1994, \"to\": 2041}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She would have qualified to represent the United States at the IAAF World Junior Championships but was too young to be eligible.\", \"from\": 2043, \"to\": 2171, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2085, \"end\": 2098, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999876676962328, \"rank\": 1.187571228752904e-05, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2106, \"end\": 2110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"IAAF\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Ath